-- int_deduped_returns.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY return_date DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    return_id,
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1

-- int_deduped_order_items.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        order_id,
        product_id,
        quantity,
        unit_price,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY order_date
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    order_id,
    product_id,
    quantity,
    unit_price
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1

-- int_category_lookup.sql
WITH source AS (

        category_id,
        name AS category_name
    FROM raw_categories
)

    category_id,
    category_name
FROM source

-- fct_returns_by_category.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        COALESCE(p.category_id, NULL) AS category_id,
        COALESCE(c.category_name, '(unknown)') AS category_name,
        oi.quantity AS items_sold,
        ri.return_id
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_category_lookup') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} ri
        ON ri.item_id = oi.item_id
)
SELECT
    category_id,
    category_name,
    SUM(items_sold) AS total_items_sold,
    COUNT(DISTINCT return_id) AS total_items_returned,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(items_sold) > 0 THEN
            ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT return_id) * 100.0 / SUM(items_sold), 2)
        ELSE 0
    END AS return_rate
FROM source
GROUP BY
    category_id,
    category_name
ORDER BY
    return_rate DESC
LIMIT 100","time":{"start":1771627028274,"end":1771627028274}}}
